  "texts": [
    "It has features of real-time collaboration and cross-device syncing.",
    "It provides the researcher with tools to annotate and cite using SmartCite.EndNote (https://endnlanguage=en): It is an AI-based reference management software with features to create a searchable personal library for all the references and reference-related materials.",
    "The EndNote Sync command synchronizes references between up to three computers, an EndNote Web library, and an iPad or iPhone.",
    "It allows the researcher to work smoothly with up to 400 co-authors and collaborators by establishing a sharing team and granting access to the synced library.",
    "The user can cite references in word processor documents."
